<div class="p-4 bg-white text-gray-dark">
    <h1 class="text-3xl text-blue-dark">Oncological Plan</h1>
    <p class="text-gray">Define your plan by adding all stages you need. <br/>
    Each stage you can also define your drug, doze, frequency and even resting period.
    <a href="https://www.cancer.org/es/cancer/como-sobrellevar-el-cancer/tomar-decisiones-sobre-el-tratamiento/planifica-programa-tratamiento.html" class=" text-blue-dark">Aqui</a>
    hay mas informaci√≥n sobre como se planifica un tratamiendo contra el cancer.
    </p>
   
    <div class="controller_panel mt-4">
        <button id="btnAddPlanStage" class="mt-2 bg-teal text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">Add a new stage to the plan</button>
        {{> dialogbox}}
        {{> toast_card}}
    </div>
    <section>
        <table id="tblTreatment">
            <caption class="text-2xl mt-6 text-blue-dark">Your Treatment Plan</caption>
            <thead>
                <th>Step</th>
                <th>Medication</th>
                <th>Dosage</th>
                <th>Guide</th>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>1</td>
                    <td>{{treatmentPlan.medicationName}}</td>
                    <td>{{treatmentPlan.dosage}}{{treatmentPlan.dosageUnit}}</td>
                    <td>{{treatmentPlan.guide}}</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>        
    </section>
</div>
